beforePurchaseContent:
Once you finalize your purchase, You are getting redirected to a page with your code.
In case you close the page before seeing the code, You can go to the email put on the Stripe Form.

If you didnt get an email, Please [Contact Us](/contact) so we can solve your problem.
---
If you have any questions before buying, Check the [FAQ](/faq) or [Contact Us](/contact)
